org.apache.hawq.pxf.service

Class BridgeOutputBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hawq.pxf.service.BridgeOutputBuilder

  • public class BridgeOutputBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Class creates the output record that is piped by the java process to the HAWQ backend. Actually, the output record is serialized and the obtained byte string is piped to the HAWQ segment. The output record will implement Writable, and the mission of BridgeOutputBuilder will be to translate a list of OneField objects (obtained from the Resolver) into an output record.
